last_episode_to_air.name: Rix Road
last_episode_to_air.overview: Cassian returns home to Ferrix, a tinderbox that is experiencing a spark of rebellion.

name: Star Wars: Andor
overview: The tale of the burgeoning rebellion against the Empire and how people and planets became involved. In an era filled with danger, deception and intrigue, Cassian Andor embarks on the path that is destined to turn him into a rebel hero.

episodes.name: Kassa
episodes.overview: Cassian Andor’s reckless search for answers about his past makes him a wanted man.

episodes.name: That Would Be Me
episodes.overview: Cassian attempts to lay low on Ferrix as agents of the law close in.

episodes.name: Reckoning
episodes.overview: Cassian’s desperation to avoid arrest leads him to a mysterious man with unknown connections.

episodes.name: Aldhani
episodes.overview: Out of options, Cassian is recruited for a dangerous mission to infiltrate an Imperial garrison.

episodes.name: The Axe Forgets
episodes.overview: Cassian must carefully navigate the distrust inherent in being the new member of a secret operation.

episodes.name: The Eye
episodes.overview: With cover from a spectacular local festival, the Aldhani mission reaches a point of no return.

episodes.name: Announcement
episodes.overview: The repercussions of the Aldhani heist reach all the way to Coruscant, while Cassian returns home.

episodes.name: Narkina 5
episodes.overview: The Empire catches up to Cassian, but are as yet unaware of his identity and past.

episodes.name: Nobody's Listening!
episodes.overview: Under intense scrutiny while imprisoned, Cassian makes allies plan an impossible escape.

episodes.name: One Way Out
episodes.overview: A rare opportunity opens and the time for Cassian and his fellow inmates to act is now.

episodes.name: Daughter of Ferrix
episodes.overview: A fugitive once more, Cassian must make his next move before it is too late.

episodes.name: Rix Road
episodes.overview: Cassian returns home to Ferrix, a tinderbox that is experiencing a spark of rebellion.
